<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>N-Order IIR Filter Assumes inputs are normalized to [-1, 1]</para>

<para>Based on the difference equation from <link xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infinite_impulse_response">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infinite_impulse_response</link> </para>
</section>
